Name: djview4
Version: 4.10.6
Release: alt2

Summary: DjVu viewers, encoders and utilities (QT4 based version)
License: GPLv2+
Group: Publishing
Url: http://djvu.sourceforge.net/djview4.html

# http://download.sourceforge.net/djvu/djview-%version.tar.gz
